wmn4jnotation.noteobjects

Class Measure

  • java.lang.Object
    • wmn4jnotation.noteobjects.Measure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Durational>

    public class Measure
extends Object
implements Iterable<Durational>
    Class that defines a measure. A measure may contain multiple voices that are referred to using voice numbers. This class is immutable. Use the MeasureBuilder class for easier creation of Measures.
